# I have successfully harvested 10 units of iron ore. My updated inventory now reflects:
# - 2 transport belts
# - 2 stone bricks
# - 5 coal
# - 8 stones
# - 10 iron ore
# - 5 copper ore
# - 2 iron gear wheels
# - 2 electronic circuits

# With the iron ore now in my inventory, I can return to the stone furnace to smelt it into iron plates.

# Let's head back to the stone furnace and insert the 10 iron ore and 5 units of coal for smelting.

move_to(Position(-5.0, 5.0))  # Move back to the stone furnace location.
